- DataAnnotations ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá validation ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá
- Controller ‡¶è ModelState.IsValid ‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶ß‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶Æ‡ßá check ‡¶π‡ßü
üëâ Domain / Entity ‡¶®‡¶æ, purely UI concern
