// 7.5 AdminResetPasswordVm
// =====================================================

/*
‡¶´‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶≤ ‡¶≤‡ßã‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶∂‡¶®:
src/OnlineBanking.Web/Models/AdminResetPasswordVm.cs
